value, so it cannot be tested.  Dump it for future tests.

Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20260322155728.81434-9-sj@kernel.org
Signed-off-by: SeongJae Park <sj@kernel.org>
Cc: Shuah Khan <shuah@kernel.org>
